{"tid":1183424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾稱梅根「討厭」？　特朗普：fake news","createTime":"2019-06-03T02:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T02:31:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ebaf170c81d9c96e5c7bb278cdcb104764e6a18","tid":1183424,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:00:47.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普國事訪問英國在即，卻傳出特朗普曾以不雅言語，形容英國哈里王子夫人梅根的流言。特朗普周日（2日）發表Twitter帖文，否認說過類似說話。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190603/s00005/0d06f9c9b3e222f0ace9bdc2045c3d52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190603%2Fs00005%2F0d06f9c9b3e222f0ace9bdc2045c3d52.jpg&h=ac79d319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事件緣於特朗普早前接受英國《太陽報》專訪的訪問錄音。當時記者稱，2016年尚未嫁入王室的梅根，曾抨擊當年正在競選總統的特朗普，稱特朗普若當選她便會選擇移居加拿大，問特朗普對此有何感想。特朗普稱，過往不知道梅根原來如此討厭（nasty），但認為梅根未來會做一個稱職的王室成員。錄音公開後，引起爭議。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普發表帖文，否認自己曾經以有關詞語形容梅根，並將矛頭指向美國有線新聞網及《紐約時報》，認為事件是美國傳媒杜撰的假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190603/s00005/1559523799910/%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E6%A2%85%E6%A0%B9%E3%80%8C%E8%A8%8E%E5%8E%AD%E3%80%8D-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E5%81%87%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190603%2Fs00005%2F1559523799910%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25A2%2585%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25A8%258E%25E5%258E%25AD%25E3%2580%258D-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=95c5c985\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190603%2Fs00005%2F1559523799910%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25A2%2585%25E6%25A0%25B9%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%25A8%258E%25E5%258E%25AD%25E3%2580%258D-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE-%